Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:32.39,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Since ancient times, the hearts of people have been charmed by beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:38.14,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,But sometimes, things that are too beautiful invite conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:40.83,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What a terrible thing this can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:45.42,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,A Cute Girl Who Comes Once Every One Hundred Thousand Years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.90,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That girl that just passed by was so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:53.76,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Seems like she's transferred into class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.07,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:02.08,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Someone new is transferring into our class today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.28,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:07.19,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,My name is Ayame Himeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:09.43,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let's get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:12.33,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:13.63,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.63,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Your desk should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.40,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's an empty desk next to Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.68,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let's have you sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:20.41,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:27.33,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let's get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.60,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.74,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about the transfer student in class A?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.12,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I know about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:37.60,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's Ayame Himeno, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:38.64,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:42.29,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:46.10,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's the kind of girl who only comes along every 10,000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.93,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Himeaya, wanna come walk home with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.26,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Himeaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:54.58,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Yep. Himeaya is short for Ayame Himeno. Himeaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.01,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That's not bad!
