Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:07.06,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,New members may line up for free photos with Himeaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.55,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's even got a fan club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.84,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's become quite the idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.56,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Himeaya, wanna go for karaoke after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.84,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Sorry. That doesn't work out for me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.16,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:23.52,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.32,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I've met you before at the intersection, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.41,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.14,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:31.10,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I'm Natsume Amano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.84,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I'm Ayame Himeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.06,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let's get along, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.13,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Likewise! And thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.85,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,It's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:46.09,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,The new girl got really popular overnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.93,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's {\i1}that{\i0} cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:49.13,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:51.13,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's gotta have pictures online.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.86,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Here she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.96,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Whoa, she's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.55,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.23,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.97,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to make a huge fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.39,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,-Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:10.20,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's gotta be the sort of cutie that only appears every 100,000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.82,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Now hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:15.97,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Natsume's the only one who deserves to be described as a "cute girl!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:17.97,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Well, just take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.55,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,How lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.77,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Muscles is having an affair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:26.59,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Y-You've got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.59,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I, Micchi, am completely devoted to Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.76,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I don't care either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.71,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She might be targeted as the next victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.03,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "targeted?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.91,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,This post has gotten popular recently.
