Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.98,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Disappearances of beautiful women?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:49.21,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,There are incidents of women suddenly going missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:51.20,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,And it's only beautiful women, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.04,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Are they being kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:53.88,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:59.16,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,According to Usuranura, supernatural phenomena might be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:04.52,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,For example, it might be a monster who rejuvenates their youth by devouring the beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:10.72,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Or it might be a reaper who leads women astray with some enchanted flute, and then steals their souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.61,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I'm not listening! I'm not listening to any of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.52,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,We can't stand for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.58,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,We must protect Himeaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:21.31,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You're just using that as an excuse to try to meet with Himeaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:24.14,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Alright, Touma! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:24.96,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.48,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Whatever! Just come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:28.22,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Hey... Akinori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.52,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I might as well come along! Whis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.26,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.67,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I hope we're not being too much of a bother to Ayame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.13,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:46.17,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's not one in 10,000! She's a beauty of one in a 100,000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.00,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Akinori, settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.79,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Shall I carry your luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.20,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear!
