Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.13,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's too perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.85,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Her moral character is also one in 100,000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:22.41,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Together with her cuteness, she's a beauty of one in 200,000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.09,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What kind of math is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:27.16,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Anyway, she's super important, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.30,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:32.65,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you, Touma! What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.16,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.45,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Who's sitting next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.50,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.72,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,A...A-A-Aye'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:44.80,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,A-Aye'm Akinori Arihoshi, a student at Momijijima Middle School!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:45.71,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,"Aye'm"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.71,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,My name is Ayame Himeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:52.25,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Ayame, we have something very important to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:08:00.25,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,...And that's why we think you might be targeted as the next victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.04,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,How do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:08.68,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That's because our job is to investigate the world's vast mysterious phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.74,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,We're the Yo-kai Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:14.24,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Detective Agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:19.26,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry for bothering you all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.93,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Not at all. It sounds really interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.93,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I'd like to join as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.96,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,ALL RIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.44,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You're very welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.64,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:32.11,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let's get along, Akinori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:35.34,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,And us too, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:42.08,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,They said that all the disappearing victims were last seen around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:46.78,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,The other thing they have in common is that they all aspired to be idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.59,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,So were they all scouted in front of the game arcade?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:54.06,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Do those scouts have some connection to the disappearances?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.83,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem to be related to the supernatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.59,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:06.54,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,{\ko196}If you ever... {\ko186}get stumped... {\ko209}I highly recommend... {\ko163}doing some squats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.02,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.43,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:17.24,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try luring out a scout while Micchi and I look from afar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.32,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.22,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.00,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.33,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:31.36,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Awesome. I've never seen Natsume like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.52,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,It's a nice style, isn't it, Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:38.32,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I've prepared it just for this moment. It's the Micchi Lovey Dovey set!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.79,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Natsume, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:40.65,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,In what way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:46.12,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Take a gander at the Slimamander! Just kidding! Ha, ha, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:48.68,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,-Hey, There's no way a scout would be impressed with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.61,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Stop taking pictures! Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:56.28,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,This'll be easy-peasy! A conspicuous outfit is gonna attract scouts in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.28,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Easy for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.92,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Geez. This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.60,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:09.18,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Would you kindly take this picture for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:10.56,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.87,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,'Scuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.54,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Which way is the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:19.39,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Oh, the station? The station is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.38,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:30.27,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can attract any scouts in this outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.64,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Maybe that outfit is way too avant-garde for this era!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.93,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You don't even know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:39.10,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Why not take a break? We’ll go buy something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:43.00,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Just get me some refreshing soda to drink, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.08,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Alrighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.92,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You can count on me to do your errands anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.08,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:50.41,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Must resist hurling insults...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.80,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.92,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I've found you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:04.92,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:09.29,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,W-What was that just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:17.84,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,With my passion and expertise, any girl can become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.56,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,W-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.41,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:29.18,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,{\ko85}This {\ko80}is {\ko104}who {\ko182}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:31.42,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Idol producer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.53,YWSerif,,0,0,0,business card,{\bord0\i1\b1\fs30\c&H000000&\1a&H35&\frz6\an9\t(\fs35.5)\move(930.2,416,988.2,412,0,2504)\blur0.51}IDOL PRODUCER
Comment: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:31.53,YWSerif,,0,0,0,business card,{\bord0\i1\b1\fs36\c&H000000&\1a&H35&\frz6\an9\pos(984.2,412)}IDOL PRODUCER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.91,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is the guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:38.48,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Mmmmm! You're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.28,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You're really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:44.27,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Your height, your hairstyle, and even your looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:48.06,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You're a really plain girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:50.99,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That sounds like faint praise to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.70,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Here's what I meant by "normal."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:12:00.76,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Like a perfect piece of porcelain pottery clay, you can be molded into any shape with infinite possibilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.72,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,But not with these on, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.72,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Away! Heh, heh, heh, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.15,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:09.40,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:14.20,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,There, there. No need to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:19.52,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Just leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:29.37,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Now let's kneed! Kneed and bake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:33.96,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I'll turn you into a shiny new porcelain idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.29,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,And it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:45.40,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What?! What just happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.93,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.75,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome our new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:59.93,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,H... H-Help me!!!
