Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.61,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Did you find my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.71,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,No. I couldn't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:08.91,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:13.18,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let's try looking somewhere else. We'll definitely find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.86,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ayame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:17.29,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... This is really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.51,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,There's no response from my Natsume Sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:21.99,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Sensor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.62,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,It's a bond of love between Natsume and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.68,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,There you go with that nonsense again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:32.28,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, this case seems to be connected to Yo-kai as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.84,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.26,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Arrived? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:40.84,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.84,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Where else do idols belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.02,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.82,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.34,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,...the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.76,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What....?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.81,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,A concert at the mall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.60,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.26,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to smile passionately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:58.11,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.25,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:01.04,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,My body is moving on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.75,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Hey everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.53,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.55,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,We're a freshly formed idol group!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:11.38,YWSpokenFuri,,0,0,0,,{\pos(689,666)}(Arita Porcelain 46)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:11.38,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,We're Aritayaki46!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:15.67,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,So, everyone, please listen to our debut song,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:21.21,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,{\ko231}{\i1}"A Young Lady's Heart Shatters Easily, {\ko71}So Do Be Careful!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:24.09,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.56,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.33,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.36,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That was Natsume's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:36.51,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,So his {\i1}bonds of love sensor{\i0} finally picked something up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:39.58,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Well let's notify the gang for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.39,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Seems like Micchi headed for the shopping mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.53,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let's go there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:49.48,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.21,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That was a great concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:54.17,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,But you girls should be capable of more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.00,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,But you were just controlling us the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:00.83,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's start practicing for some new performances!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.71,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Lessons! Lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.12,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Ah! Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.56,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Who's that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:13.48,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's the scout that has something to do with the disappearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:14.64,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let's go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.20,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.55,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.85,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.36,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,"Bonds of love?" Looks more like a stalker's stubbornness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:30.56,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.11,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Who was that purple person just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.31,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You were able to see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.41,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.69,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,One! Two! One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.33,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Smile and turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.00,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Yes! And stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:45.30,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Hold it, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.48,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You're not smiling enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.81,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Ewww. This is humiliating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.89,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:52.79,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:04.51,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.96,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,How the heck does that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.07,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,E-Everyone's here! Ayame is here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:11.98,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:15.20,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You're the one who kidnapped all those girls, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.40,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,G-Give me back my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:19.07,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.98,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I won't let you interrupt my lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:26.10,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You've come to steal away my idols, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.37,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.79,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:36.99,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,He was a Yo-kai all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:40.04,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.66,mask,,0,0,0,BC2 SS mask,{\an7\p1\c&H000000&}m 141 398 l 436 276 464 322 170 448{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.66,YWScaryDialog,,0,0,0,BC2 SS,{\frz22\fs70\pos(324,396)\blur2}Shadowside
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.66,YWScaryDialog,,0,0,0,BC2 SS yo-kai,{\frz25\fry3\frx4\fs90\blur0.3\bord0\c&H000000&\pos(812,514.668)}Yo-kai KamaDOUma
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:43.43,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Umm... It's the Yo-kai Kamadoma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:46.81,YWScaryDialog,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.08,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.78,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,{\ko80}Possession! {\ko133}Genma Benkei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.92,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Lend me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.98,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,{\ko182}Benkei... {\ko164}has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.95,YWScaryDialog,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Producing idols is my mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:14.24,YWScaryDialog,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Those who stand in my way shall be burned in the fires of my kiln!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.34,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Natsume! Hey, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:17.62,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.48,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm finally back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.41,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.12,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what's with those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.54,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Did you get a makeover?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.88,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,It's not like I wanted to wear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.26,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive him for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.70,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Micchi! Shadowside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.45,YWScaryDialog,,0,0,0,,Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.63,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Alright, Micchi, finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.46,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.24,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect Natsume to be this intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:54.24,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,She's scary when she's angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:54.80,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.31,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You can't make me give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:07.39,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I must produce the best idol group ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:12.11,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I won't ever give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.43,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kamamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.68,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You're Kamamoto the producer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:23.64,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,We were so worried when we heard that you went missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.30,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.13,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Who are you girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.19,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:31.76,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,It's been more than twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.21,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Twenty years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:38.09,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,You're the first idol group I produced for!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.31,YWSpokenFuri,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,666)}(Seto Ceramic 46)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.31,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,The founding members of Setoyaki46!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.08,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Hana! Yuki! Tsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.42,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:50.21,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I was raised in a family that made pottery for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:51.81,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,But then, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:56.19,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I found something that moved my heart even more than pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.49,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,And it was idol groups!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:01.68,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I'll create Japan's most glamorous idol group ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:05.06,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,And to fulfill that dream, I produced for a group.
