Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:31.11,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,They beat us and forced us to shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.34,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,And then my dream was shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:38.54,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,There was nothing left but despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.05,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,No. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:47.53,YWScaryDialog,,0,0,0,,Next time, I will absolutely create the best idol group ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.30,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:54.96,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,So the reason you disappeared was because you became a Yo-kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.33,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you took things too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:58.70,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.89,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,So I've failed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:04.49,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.45,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,If only I was able to do a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.04,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,There's no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.17,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:14.42,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Kamamoto, you helped us so much back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:17.36,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't still hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:21.35,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Well, it was regrettable that we were forced to shut down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:24.52,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,But we shined beautifully while it lasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:27.61,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,We never told you before, but we're finally telling you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.71,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Mr. Kamamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:36.75,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,So everything I've done wasn't for nothing after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.33,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.57,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.93,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry for the trouble I caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:48.31,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I am now retiring from being a producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.30,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:51.88,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,May I have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.96,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to be an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.30,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,But I lacked confidence and gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:58.16,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.49,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,When I stood on that stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:04.40,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,hearing the audience cheer me on gave me the confidence I needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:07.73,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kamamoto, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.70,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Please be my producer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:10.17,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.56,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Got it! Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:18.37,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I'll turn you into a shining star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:26.92,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,What do we do now that Ayame knows all about Yo-kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:31.51,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Let her be a member of the Yo-kai Detective Agency, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:33.37,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I vote yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:37.00,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,But dealing with Yo-kai can be dangerous as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.69,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll do all I can to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.15,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:41.88,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:43.96,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Just come have some fun with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:45.21,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:46.61,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Ayame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:47.88,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,We've got to help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:50.46,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,Just cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:53.99,YWSpokenDefault,,0,0,0,,I've been studying karate, you know.
